  *"Updated by someone else — reloaded"*
- Auto-dismiss after 4 seconds.
- Do not show a modal.

When a command is rejected with an invalid transition:

- Show an inline banner: *"[rejection_reason]"*
- Persist until dismissed (× button).

### G3 — Connection status indicator

In the app header (operator view only, not TV display):

- Green dot: FastAPI reachable, Supabase Realtime connected.
- Amber dot + *"Reconnecting..."*: either FastAPI or Realtime
  temporarily unreachable, commands queued.
- Red dot + *"Offline"*: both unreachable for > 60 seconds.

Do not use a toast for this — it is persistent status, not a
one-time event.

